<p style="font-size:20px"> <em> One day, while casually strolling through the neighborhood, your eye catches on <br>an old scrap of scroll lying on the floor. You pick it up and examine it. </em> </p>
<img src="scrollp3.png" class="center">
</br> 
</br>
 
<p style="font-size:20px"> <em> The day after finding the paper, you hear a broadcast over the radio. </em> </p>
<p style="font-size:16px"> "To whoever finds my journal, I hope you can take away three things. First, look at how the lines are drawn. <br>Take the first of the shortest common unit of time. Second, without the number, what do I want you to take away? <br>Finally, string together the smallest pieces from the east. Good luck, my friend. It's up to you to find the final missing piece." </p>
</br>

 Answer: 
 <input type="text" id="p5_input">
 <button type="button" id="p5_button" style="height:22px;width:80px" onclick="guess()"> Submit </button>
 
